American rapper, Radric Davis, popularly known as Gucci Mane, gifted his wife, Keyshia Ka’oir, one million dollars cash on her 37th birthday. The Jamaican model took to her Instagram story on Friday to share a video of herself receiving the gift from her husband at her birthday party. In appreciation to her husband for the gift, Keyshia wrote, “One of my birthdays ever. Thank you hubby.” The rapper also took to his Instagram page to celebrate his wife’s birthday. Gucci Mane wrote on Thursday, “Happy Birthday to my wife, the most beautiful woman in the world and the best thing ever came into my life. “I love you Mrs Davis forever. I appreciate and will never take you for granted. I got the perfect wife and family and I got your back for life.” Still hailing his wife on Friday, the rapper wrote, “Behind every strong black man is a strong black woman. Thank you for staying down when everyone turned their back. “I got the smartest, prettiest and most loyal wife in the world and I’ll spoil her for life.” The couple married in 2017 and welcomed their son, Ice, in 2020. Copyright PUNCH. All rights reserved. This material, and other digital content on this website, may not be reproduced, published, broadcast, rewritten or redistributed in whole or in part without prior express written permission from PUNCH. Contact: theeditor@punchng.com